summary:
In my media studies I’ve been doing some readings on fandoms, and found this little quote: 
“The culture of a fandom is just as...
body:
In my media studies I’ve been doing some readings on fandoms, and found this little quote:

“The culture of a fandom is just as integral to the fandom as the relationship of the fan to the text itself”

I can’t help but get a little proud of how incredible our fandom is, our “culture” is so supportive, positive, funny and bright. I’m so proud to be a part of it.
